window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>From USA Today Bestselling Author Laura Scott</i></b><br> <br> <i>Search and rescue and love…</i><br> <br> <i>A search for the truth…</i><br> <br> Libby Tolliver doesn’t hesitate to call Shane Sullivan and his K9 Bryce to help find her missing grandfather. What should be a simple search turns dark when someone shoots at them. Soon Libby realizes that her grandfather hasn’t left of his own accord, someone had taken him away from her. But why?<br> <br> Shane Sullivan always expects the worst of every situation and searching for Libby’s grandfather is no different. As his K9 Bryce follows the scent trail, danger stalks them at every turn. All too soon he realizes secrets from the past have risen to the surface. Can he and Bryce keep Libby and her grandfather safe long enough to have a future?</p>"; 
